---
title: Shrimp and Kale Chow Mein with Bacon Crumble
description: Chow Mein is a classic Chinese dish that has been adopted around the world. Chow Mein simply means ‘fried noodles’. Our version contains tender kale, sweet shrimp and a salty bacon crumble, all tossed in a delicious sauce!
